      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/1/1",
      "text": [
        " الْفِتْنَةِ كَابْنِ اللَّبُونِ، لاَ ظَهْرٌ فَيُرْكَبَ، وَلاَ ضَرْعٌ فَيُحْلَبَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "1. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: During civil disturbance be like an adolescent camel [1] who has neither a back strong enough for riding nor udders for milking."
        ]
      }
